===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{context|intransitive|lang=en}} To [[write]] or [[speak]] after the manner of an epitaph.
#* Bishop Hall
#*: The common in their speeches '''epitaph''' upon him {{...}} "He lived as a wolf and died as a dog."
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To [[commemorate]] by an epitaph.
#* G. Harvey
#*: Let me be '''epitaphed''' the inventor of English hexameters.

